Day 21: Trust the Team!
🤝 "Trust is the backbone of a high-performing team!"  
👉 Tip: Show the team you trust them to make decisions. When you trust them, they’ll trust each other.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
-----

🧠 Poll: "How much trust do you place in your team to make decisions?"  
1. Complete trust 🤝  
2. Mostly trust 💪  
3. Could trust more 🔧  
4. Trust is a challenge 🏴‍☠️
